h you","video":{"src":"/1.mp4"}},{"title":"Psalm 46:5","description":"God is within her, she will not fall","video":{"src":"/2.mp4"}},{"title":"Psalms 9:2","description":"I will be glad and rejoice in you","video":{"src":"/3.mp4"}},{"title":"Psalm 23:6","description":"Surely your goodness and love","video":{"src":"/4.mp4"}}],"className":"bg-background"},"faq":{"id":"faq","title":"Frequently Asked Questions","description":"Everything you need to know about creating your Bible video","items":[{"question":"What makes these videos special?","answer":"Each video is custom-created from your story. It is a one-of-a-kind gift rooted in Scripture, prayer, and genuine care - designed to bring comfort and peace to your heart."},{"question":"How long does it take to receive the video?","answer":"Your finished Bible video is delivered in just 2-5 minutes. We use advanced AI technology to create your personalized video quickly while maintaining the highest quality."},{"question":"What themes can I create videos about?","answer":"Anything that honors God: birthdays, anniversaries, weddings, grief, encouragement, testimonies, or prayers for strength and healing. Share your heart, and we'll create a video that speaks to it."},{"question":"How will I receive the finished video?","answer":"You will receive a secure link via email to play your Bible video on any device and to easily share it with family and friends."},{"question":"Can I use the video at church or events?","answer":"Yes, you may share and play your Bible video at private events and church gatherings to inspire and comfort others."},{"question":"What if generation fails?","answer":"If your video fails to generate due to a technical issue, you will not lose any credits. We automatically refund your credits, and you can try again immediately."}],"buttons":[{"title":"Create Your Bible Video","url":"/ai-video-generator","target":"_self","variant":"default","icon":"Play"}],"className":"bg-background"},"cta":{"id":"cta","title